[['NewsAPI.get_recent_news', {'name': 'NewsAPI.get_recent_news', 'description': 'Get recent news articles based on specified keywords and time range.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'keywords', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the keywords to search for in news articles.'}, {'name': 'time_range', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the time range for the news articles, e.g., 1 year.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'the list of news articles, each article is a dict with title and content.'}]}], ['SurveyAPI.get_satisfaction_data', {'name': 'SurveyAPI.get_satisfaction_data', 'description': 'Get consumer satisfaction data for a specified industry and time range.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'industry', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the industry to get satisfaction data for.'}, {'name': 'time_range', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the time range for the data, e.g., 1 year.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'satisfaction_data', 'description': 'the satisfaction data, a dict with industry and time range.'}]}], ['CaseStudyAPI.get_consumer_behavior_case', {'name': 'CaseStudyAPI.get_consumer_behavior_case', 'description': 'Get consumer behavior case studies for a specified company and time range.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the name of the company to get case studies for.'}, {'name': 'time_range', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the time range for the case studies, e.g., 1 year.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'case_studies', 'description': 'the list of case studies, each case study is a dict with company name and analysis.'}]}], ['AnalysisAPI.analyze_marketing_strategy', {'name': 'AnalysisAPI.analyze_marketing_strategy', 'description': 'Analyze the marketing strategy of a specified company based on consumer behavior data.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the name of the company to analyze.'}, {'name': 'time_range', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the time range for the analysis, e.g., 1 year.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'marketing_strategy', 'description': 'the analyzed marketing strategy, a dict with company name and strategy.'}]}], ['RecommendationAPI.provide_analysis_tips', {'name': 'RecommendationAPI.provide_analysis_tips', 'description': 'Provide tips on how to conduct consumer behavior analysis in the real economy.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'tips', 'description': 'the list of tips for conducting consumer behavior analysis.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
